Username: ##Required - Valid username in an email format. Must be unique in the system. DO NOT change username for existing employee, unless the User ID column is column is provided; otherwise new employee will be created.##
First Name: ## Required - Must contain value. No space as a single value. At least one character and maximum 50 characters ##
Last Name: ## Required - Must contain value. No space as a single value. At least one character and maximum 50 characters ##
Email Address: ## Required - Must contain valid email address ##
Hire Date: ##Optional - Must be a valid date. Format is MMM-DD-YYYY (JUL-14-2015). Default is current date at the time of import##
Invite: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE to indicate whether to send a registration invitation after import. Default is 'False'##
Team Name: ##Optional - Valid team name. Default is 'System Default' team##
MFA Secret: ##Optional - Can accept secret of length 16 or 26 or 32. Characters allowed 'A-Z' '0-9'##
MFA Time Period: ##Optional - Can accept time step between 15 - 300. Characters allowed '0-9'. Default is 30##
Can Be Coached Or Evaluated: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'TRUE'.Enables the employee to be evaluated if your tenant is licensed and configured for CXone Quality Management (QM)##
Can Be Scheduled: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'TRUE'. Enables the employee to be scheduled if tenant is licensed and configured for CXone Workforce Management (WFM).##
Can Be Recorded: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'TRUE'. Enables the employee's voice to be recorded if tenant is configured for CXone Recording.##
Can Be Analyzed: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'TRUE'. Enables the employee to be recorded if tenant is configured for CXone Analytics.##
Status: ##Any values in the Status column will be ignored and the value will be set to “NOT YET INVITED”##
Virtual Agent Enabled: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'TRUE'. Enables the employee to be a virtual agent.##
Virtual Agent Type: ##Optional - Set to Digital Bot, Digital Survey, or OFF. Default is 'OFF'. If Virtual Agent Enabled is true, this field identifies the type of virtual agent.##
Can View BI Reports: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'TRUE'. Enables the employee to view BI reports.##
Can Be Recorded Screen: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'TRUE'. Enables the employee's screen to be recorded if tenant is configured for CXone Screen Recording.##
Login Authenticator Name: ##Optional - Must contain valid login authenticator name.##
User ID: ##Optional - Must contain valid UUID.  This value must be provided if Username is being changed for existing employee ##
Deactivate: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE to indicate whether to deactivate an existing user. Default is 'False'##
Agent Integrations: ##Optional - Set to TRUE or FALSE. Default is 'FALSE'. Enables the employee for agent integrations .##
